Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:00.22,geciCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想摆个姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远离濑户几十里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降生未久彩之国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽遇鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗争激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十有四岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走在荆棘遍布的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱之路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然来信打扰 真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 从很久以前就开始喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十一话 无谓的恋爱骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 今天的作业都做完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难...难道 这个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然来信打扰 真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后 我在焚化炉旁等你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有意的话 请你过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生到现在 我还是第一次收到这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来 我的幼稚园和小学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一副不受欢迎的冬天海峡景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.00,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界的中心大声呼唤着 "我不受欢迎"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.30,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}泼上不受欢迎果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连"不受欢迎同盟"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都年年获得优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却收到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now 现在 我能行...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就从男厕所的单间里传来"我可以 我能行"的喊声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OH YES
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就排泄的这么顺畅吗 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 遇到什么好事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管我完全没有意思要背叛嫁给我的小灿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但第一次收到情书 我真是太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情真不错嘛 蛀虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 蛀虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是有什么事瞒着我和灿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄有事瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉本小姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说 仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我都说了 没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连本小姐都不能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是好了伤疤忘了痛的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蛀虫的口袋里有这样一封谜样的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后 我在焚化炉旁等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有意的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这不是情书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是情书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 居然也收到情书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情书啊 真恼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁写的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:54.43,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小留奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要监视焚化炉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿小姐 小声点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仆人那家伙不知道这信已经被我们看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是否出现在这里 就能看出他到底花不花心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩哪 今天终于能拆穿满潮永澄的不诚实了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人期待呢 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连你们也在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小声点 会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有偷窥的嗜好 真恼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连巡和番长也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我来巡逻焚化炉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚好路过 别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我... 先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿 你就一点也不在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种事情果然不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 永澄来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我来得早了些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信里也没写寄信人的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个花心大萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿 快忘了那个没节操的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和同是鱼人的我结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫? 鱼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 说过多少次叫你注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是好好拒绝对方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那样做肯定符合礼数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 永澄说要拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然永澄的心里还是有我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是拒绝掉还真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留奈的爸爸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又穿水手服来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你在干什么啊 留奈爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近常来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送出那封信的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要看看你小子对灿到底是不是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Game over了 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到 你还真敢大晃大摆地出现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我是准备回绝掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 留奈爸爸根本就没必要穿上水手服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多说无用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢背叛我的灿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我吃掉他 藤代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿 用超音波前先打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了隐藏鱼人的身份 这也是迫不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿 原来你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那说话也就方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.87,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}攻\N击\N回\N避\N机\N能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:45.95,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}L\NV\N4\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌人袭击 不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是这小子的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子收到情书 马上就大晃大摆地过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是这样一种人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才被超音波攻击 我现在什么都听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有可以说服我的理由 我现在就听听看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就要抹杀你 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些白痴白痴老爸's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚过来看你是不是又和留奈的爸爸勾结起来做什么蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要陷害中学生玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 到底谁是花心大萝卜的人渣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你和酒吧的明美发展得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲 当着灿的面就不要说这种事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就如你所愿 我们到那边去好好谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是血腥的战场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 不要再穿着水手服出现在本小姐面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个变态爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得... 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不用说 我都明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 大清早的出什么事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很没精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 因为我实在太没出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次收到情书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一个人开心得晕头转向的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明有个那么好的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只有一瞬间 我也不该觉得自己很行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不过是一次的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是情书的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你这么消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都觉得不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟有一半是我丈夫的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如需选购...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人鱼的魔法药水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝了它以后就能体验到受欢迎的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎人鱼的东西喝下去每次都不会有什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人鱼的秘药对人类来说效果太强了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次就服用少量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果只有一天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得没什么效果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么了 小灿的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄已经成为一个好男儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直太合我口味了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿还满足不了你的吧 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 我来一点点教你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.23,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}容量Over
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 我...还有课要上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上我的单独指导课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不... 不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 记得班会不要迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 朱丽叶 下次我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 迟到也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么迟到了 仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 留奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和本小姐结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛀虫 昨天被教训完了还敢花心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么漂亮的贝壳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还闪闪发光啊 快来 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 卷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么啦 小灿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 太有男人味了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说 太符合我胃口了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难...难道说 这就是秘药的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小灿她们看来 我现在一定是个帅男
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个秘药... 就是媚药啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里 吵什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 要是连灿的爸爸都迷上我了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事吗 豪三郎老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家女儿 本大爷收下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我去死 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么 满潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢飞到我这来 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊 三河
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就一直看你不顺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天更是特别的不顺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neo Tiger 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又突然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难 难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子 你看我现在到底怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这事平时也有发生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是别攻击永澄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巡眼里我到底是什么样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这个秘药的效果是受女性欢迎被男人憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不管哪边都很不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:42.56,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}特\N殊\N功\N能\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:43.23,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}L\NV\N4
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌人 数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被憎恨那边比较泼辣点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁泼辣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要送你下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你的骨髓都吸干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低头就死吧 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热 好热 热热热热...不要烧我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知火同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧 这个神秘集团是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 满潮永...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无...无懈可击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我输了 任你处置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底把我看成什么样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要烧死你 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...小灿的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 永澄 事情变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您给了我什么秘药啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真没想到效果会这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天药效就过去了 所以原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 哪怕只有一个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘药 药效过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 永澄 怎么不上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚饭是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈能生出你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前不都说不好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为永澄是个更冷漠散漫 双目无神的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我开始害怕明天变回原来的自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的浴室真是比以前好多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 今天还真是凄惨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然受女生欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只有一天的话 什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 绝不是什么低贱之事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 卷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来帮你刷背的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到我不好意思的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没有看到永澄的"卷贝"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了 快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体我自己会洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿 留奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷背...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来帮你了 仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连巡和不知火都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然巡不认认真真帮你洗净所有地方的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了 也就不奢求擦背了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等...等一下 你们这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 偶尔这样也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 交给巡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点从浴缸里出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 快让我们欣赏一下你那有男人味的裸体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都知道自己到底在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉的卷贝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本小姐会帮你把全身洗得干干净净的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢 这个给巡做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样 我还是很会帮人洗澡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的眼神都不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子欲望还真不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个混蛋 竟敢让灿穿着泳衣帮你刷背
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救我 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你看你看 我这身体美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢...谢谢你 小灿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的本小姐到底是怎么了 竟然会觉得仆人有男人味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再受欢迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟前天内容相同的信出现在鞋箱中...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还来践踏男人的纯情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:41.10,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报不会有错的吧 卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛀虫那家伙今早确实收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 这次一定要弄出一个真正的地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在这里藏着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那边去 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我笑话就这么有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 高兴吧永澄 那封信是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点忘了灿大小姐 去开始新的恋爱吧 蛀虫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了哦 来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别藏了 过快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为... 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是 上次公园里的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她是这所学校的学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个打扮去告白一定会成功的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我保证的 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命短暂 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄	
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是站在巡的身边 是班里最没有存在感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是在这里看着永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来... 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎... 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子里一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得说些什么 我得说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:18:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 请和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人喜欢的是小灿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是喜欢这个混蛋的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是被爸爸叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户灿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你向我告白 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由于种种原因 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难...难道 我向濑户同学告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还被永澄看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:46.42,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里为私家领域 请遵守交通规则 不要超速行驶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我鼓起勇气挑战一生一次的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春这个大混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的哦 他们不知道你是班长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就这样表演完全不同的另一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是有出路的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:18:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES Amazones
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为大家说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.31,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}堆积在心中的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.50,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}得不到回报的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得不到回报的少女 其堆积在心中的压力正在班长体内膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作一鼓不可思议的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.19,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不思议能量 充电中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她变身为最后的女战士(Amazones)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES Amazones
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES Amazones
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的女战士 参见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人是只喜欢女生 做为女贞一族最后的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被我 最后的女战士盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最后一定会成为我的 濑户灿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再见面的时候 我会亲自把你收下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好期待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES Amazones
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她是Amazones啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了 最后的女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一辈子我都不摘眼镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.14,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}眼镜 一生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No 眼镜 No life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡警来为你 调查真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 把你知道的事情全部说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据巡的调查结果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和磯野第八中学教师的关系非同一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实交待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 无论如何你都不打算说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你肚子饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 特制猪排盖饭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡亲手做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份思念是多么...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子见到你现在这样 一定会非常伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让自己的亲身儿子伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会全部说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个人又深沉 是个好男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄似乎也很有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他有这个意愿的话那不如就顺水推舟...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀讨厌 我还只是个女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巡到那个时候就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:54.60,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想象力太丰富 容量超载了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 现在不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:22:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之只要巡还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.99,0:23:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不允许学校的相关人员有不正当性关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让巡来教你"健全的男女交往"的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:08.55,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我乃正义!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正当交往 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡要拘留你们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好窄的秘室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱形... 原来是钱形干的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们分开关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又有一个歪风邪气被我修正了
